name: Cute Tumblr Dashedit
css:
@-moz-document url-prefix('http://www.tumblr.com/'), url-prefix('https://www.tumblr.com/')   {            #dashboard_index, #dashboard_edit_post, #dashboard_submissions, #dashboard_drafts, #dashboard_post_queue, #dashboard_followers, #dashboard_members{    background-image:url('http://i53.tinypic.com/2jfxirk.png') !important;    background-repeat:repeat !important;    background-attachment: fixed;    background-color:#FFCCD1 !important;    background-position:top !important    }                #dashboard_index div.l-content, #dashboard_submissions div.l-content, #dashboard_drafts div.l-content, #dashboard_post_queue div.l-content, #dashboard_members #left_column, #right_column {background-color: transparent !important;}

div.l-content.l-content.l-content {    background: rgba(254,247,239,0.7) !important;    }                #dashboard_edit_post{    background-color: #FFCCD1 !important    }                #right_column .dashboard_nav_item {    border-bottom:0px solid #eee !important;    background-image url(http://www.doodlerblog.com/wp-content/uploads/362/marker-doodle.jpg)  !important        }                #right_column .dashboard_nav_item .dashboard_nav_title,                        #right_column .dashboard_nav_item .dashboard_nav_title a,                        #right_column .dashboard_nav_item a,                        #right_column .dashboard_nav_item ul.dashboard_subpages,                        #right_column .dashboard_nav_item ul.dashboard_subpages li a {                            color:#96a59a !important;        }                #right_column .dashboard_nav_item ul.dashboard_subpages li a.tracked_tag_control {                            color:#888 !important ;                        }                #right_column .dashboard_nav_item #dashboard_controls_radar_media_fold {                            background: none !important;                        }        #left_column #posts .notification .avatar {                            border-color:transparent !important;                            background-color:#FFCCD1 !important;                            }                #left_column #posts .notification .avatar:hover {opacity:1 !important;}        .post{opacity:1 !important; border-bottom:0px !important; color:#555555}    .post:hover{opacity:1 !important}    .permalink{background-color: #ffffff !important; background-image:http://www.brandbuildsell.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/08/gypsy-garden-tumblr-background.jpg !important}    .active{background-color:#f9ccc9 !important; color:#96a59a !important;}    .nav_item_nipple{display:none !important}    .nav_menu{background-color:#e7bcc6 !important; border-bottom:0px !important; color:#96a59a !important;}            #nav .nav_item.active,    #nav .nav_item .nav_menu,    #nav .nav_item .nav_item_nipple .nav_item_nipple_pixel {    background-color:#fddcd5 !important;    background-image:none !important;    border:0px !important;    color:#96a59a !important;    }                #nav .nav_item .nav_menu {    border-bottom:0px !important    }                #nav .nav_item .nav_menu a {    color:#e7bcc6 !important;    border-top-color:#322115 !important;    }        #nav .nav_item .nav_menu a:hover {    color:#fbfbfb !important;}            .dashboard_switch_blog_menu_header{    background-color:#17130d !important;    color:#777 !important;    }        .dashboard_switch_blog_menu_item{    background-color:#ffffff !important;    color:#777 !important;    border:0px !important    }        .dashboard_switch_blog_menu_footer{    background-color:#ffffff !important;    color:#777 !important;    }        .dashboard_switch_blog_menu_wrapper{    background-color:#ffffff !important;    }                #new_post_notice_container{    color:#fff !important    }                #new_post_notice_container a{    color:#fff !important    }                #dashboard_switch_blog_menu_current,    #dashboard_switch_blog_arrow_and_divider,    #dashboard_switch_blog_arrow_current    {background-image:none !important}            #footer{    background: #F778A1 !important;    background-image:http://www.brandbuildsell.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/08/gypsy-garden-tumblr-background.jpg !important    }            ol#posts li.post.new_post {    background: #ffffff url('http://img441.imageshack.us/img441/3355/iconsreallll.png') center center no-repeat;    }                img[src*="http://assets.tumblr.com/images/new_post_icons_no_labels.png"] {        width:0;        height:70px;        padding-right:250px;        opacity: 0;    }  .new_post_label{    font-size:14px !important;    padding-top:5px !important;    font-family:Georgia, Times New Roman, sans-serif !important;    font-style:italic !important;    text-transform: none !important;    color:#Ffffff !important;    letter-spacing:1px !important          }        #left_column #posts .notification {                            background-color:#fef7ef !important;                            color:#FFCCCC !important;                            border-bottom-color: #FFCCCC !important                        }                #left_column #posts .notification .block {                                color:#FFCCCC !important;                            }                #left_column #posts .notification.alt {                            background-color: #fef7ef !important;    border-bottom-color: #ffcccc !important                        }        #left_column #posts .notification.last_notification,                        #left_column #posts .notification.single_notification {                            border-bottom-color:#FFCCCC !important;                        }        #left_column #posts .notification a {                            color:#68574a !important;                            border-bottom:0px !important;                        }        #left_column #posts .notification blockquote {                            border-left-color:#eee !important;                        }                #left_column #posts .notification .avatar {                            border-color:transparent !important;                            background-color:#fbfbfb !important;                        }                #left_column #posts .notification .avatar:hover{                        }    .notification_type_icon{display:none !important}            h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6{color:#F8EBE6 !important}        }
